Pepe Clan has been established since a thousand years ago. Firstly founded by the King Pepelenials, known as The Hail King of The Kek Universe, Peacelover from The South, Protector of the Earth. He has the special entity who can live timelessly through the universe. He guards and observes all the universe that exist to bring Equilibrium of Peace, Harmony in time, and Eternal love.
